parcel.description: Want your art featured in the Community Gallery?  Submit in our [Discord](https://discord.gg/vapSENqUpe).  There is no cost to be featured and imnotArt does not take any commission on sales.  The space will change every week for our Thursday events.  To learn more about the imnotArt community join our Discord or visit our website, [http://imnotart.com](http://imnotart.com).
